Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:07.35,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:13.61,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:18.90,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:25.41,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:32.04,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:38.38,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,751)\be1}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:47.10,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:53.36,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:03:00.11,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:06.37,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:12.25,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And rise back up again and again and again
