Dialogue: 7,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h is good.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it can't win.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it can beat {\i1}CROW{\i0}\h and {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:17.74,0:00:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, with a majority vote of 3 for Win and 4 for Lose,
Dialogue: 7,0:00:25.42,0:00:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi Muto's {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h will not be serialized...
Dialogue: 7,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 7,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Oonishi?
Dialogue: 7,0:00:34.38,0:00:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't pass Ashirogi here, they won't be able to draw for Jack anymore, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the reason for this vote.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to change my vote!
Dialogue: 7,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Change it?
Dialogue: 7,0:00:50.58,0:00:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 7,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it 4 against 3.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Ashirogi passes, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:00:56.92,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous for us to let Ashirogi go based on a vote in the first place!
Dialogue: 7,0:01:02.65,0:01:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take better care of our authors!
Dialogue: 7,0:01:05.19,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We're in a position to influence the lives of our authors.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:11.05,0:01:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 7,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a different story if the vote was 7 to 0,
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.52,0:01:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to abandon our authors over such a \Nnarrow margin may not be the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heishi?
Dialogue: 7,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I judged they would lose,
Dialogue: 7,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we should leave this decision to the readers, after all.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:27.74,0:01:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cast my vote for them to win.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want them to win.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:35.15,0:01:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the decision to the readers, huh?
Dialogue: 7,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we've always done.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also change my vote to win.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ep title}
Dialogue: 7,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 7,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 7,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:35.06,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h will be serialized!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the news for now! Details will come later!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:43.94,0:03:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to celebrating! I'll get the cake!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:46.82,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, it looks like you've got yourself a serialization.
Dialogue: 7,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll congratulate you, just for today.
Dialogue: 7,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can compete with you again!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bring it on!
Dialogue: 7,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to your first chapter!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:06.86,0:04:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our real battle begins.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you that we were able to come this far!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 7,0:04:17.04,0:04:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we saw your name listed as a Tezuka prize finalist at a convenience store back in middle school,
Dialogue: 7,0:04:22.97,0:04:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,650)}we made you our rival and pledged to overtake you.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:29.15,0:04:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to stop {\i1}Tanto{\i0}\h and aim higher because you were there as our rival.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi and I are fated rivals.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eternal rivals".
Dialogue: 7,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be written as "formidable \Nenemy" but pronounced as "friend".
Dialogue: 7,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 7,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to put everything we've\N learned into this one, so we'll win for sure!
Dialogue: 7,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have confidence in it, then?
Dialogue: 7,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall return to work.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rival, huh.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting all tense now.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:08.72,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put the complicated stuff on hold for now and get to celebrating!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's mine.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro gets the piece with the chocolate.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.63,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 7,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.72,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Azuki's homemade cake!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:27.18,0:05:31.06,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both really happy with being serialized in Jack!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 7,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's inside...
Dialogue: 7,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A USB stick?
Dialogue: 7,0:05:35.74,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miho prepared this kind of surprise?
Dialogue: 7,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akito, bring your computer over here.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, is it alright for the two of us to see it?
Dialogue: 7,0:05:45.55,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a bit embarrassing, but it's fine.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it's fine!
Dialogue: 7,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{5:53}To Mashiro
Dialogue: 7,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, your birthday present made me really happy.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 7,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I received a drawing from Mashiro, the manga artist,
Dialogue: 7,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a vocal present, as a voice actress.
Dialogue: 7,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just her voice?
Dialogue: 7,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a video letter.
Dialogue: 7,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Kaya.
Dialogue: 7,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear it.
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{crhistmas shit, do i have to karaoke this}
Dialogue: 7,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she gotten better at singing?
Dialogue: 7,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she did say she was going to learn how to sing.
Dialogue: 7,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's been an editor change?
Dialogue: 7,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief Editor noticed, after all...
Dialogue: 7,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, can I have a moment?
Dialogue: 7,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 7,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 7,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you do something you need to apologize for?
Dialogue: 7,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... for {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h!
Dialogue: 7,0:08:23.16,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I submitted it as if it was all my work, but I had Hattori help me...
Dialogue: 7,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve to be removed from it!
Dialogue: 7,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not a bad thing to receive the advice of others.
Dialogue: 7,0:08:37.66,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that is only if you are willing to cast aside your pride and listen carefully to the person offering advice.
Dialogue: 7,0:08:45.12,0:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This serialization is a result of you taking action to help Ashirogi.
Dialogue: 7,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 7,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 7,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could tell that Hattori played a large part in it.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he also understands Ashirogi well.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to leave them to him.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I suppose it's time for you to return the favor.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he's having some troubles. {}
Dialogue: 7,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We're getting a new editor?
Dialogue: 7,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 7,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we just got serialized...
Dialogue: 7,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you should be happy.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should?
Dialogue: 7,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori?!
Dialogue: 7,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting Hattori back?!
Dialogue: 7,0:09:36.11,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miura, you've done so much for us,
Dialogue: 7,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we finally got this far together...
Dialogue: 7,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's okay to be happy.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura...
Dialogue: 7,0:09:45.59,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is frustrating to get a different assignment now,
Dialogue: 7,0:09:49.58,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it worked out so that Hattori and I have swapped places.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:53.57,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in charge of {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 7,0:09:57.94,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h a big hit with Hattori!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'll duke it out!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:05.99,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 7,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely won't lose!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you or to Niizuma!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Akina Aiko!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We won't lose, either!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.46,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin, I'm going to our studio!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.26,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:15.61,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice... it feels like a man's world!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 7,0:10:27.57,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for me to be Ashirogi's editor?
Dialogue: 7,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be happy!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:10:34.88,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I did all that... but now it \Nseems selfish, and I feel bad about it...
Dialogue: 7,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too serious.
Dialogue: 7,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, Ashirogi overcame some huge obstacles.
Dialogue: 7,0:10:49.12,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Fukuda understands this and \Ndoesn't get any crazy ideas...
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{10:55}
Dialogue: 7,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose, either!
Dialogue: 7,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you take a break, at least for today?
Dialogue: 7,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets head over to Ashirogi's now!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:08.26,0:11:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 7,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been waiting for you all this time!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the earlier the better.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from kids to housewives are snatching up Otter figures!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I did hear some rumors about that!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's time for "This week's Aoki Kou!"
Dialogue: 7,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki wants...
Dialogue: 7,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants...
Dialogue: 7,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want...
Dialogue: 7,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An Otter figure!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Otter figure!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll sign one of each kind and give them all to her personally!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:43.37,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... she told me to give it to her editor.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 7,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:51.91,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the {\i1}Otters{\i0}\h anime is doing well.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 7,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, well...
Dialogue: 7,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my editor about this, but...
Dialogue: 7,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 7,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about that "secret" Otter figure?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:04.86,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You can exchange the hands with real limestone!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:08.20,0:12:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one. My assistant really wants it.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your assistant?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yoshida? What's this all about?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:18.92,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yoshida?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats on your serialization!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, I'm glad to be working with you again!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 7,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, too.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to look over it again, starting with chapter one.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the first chapter can get first place.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 7,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 7,0:12:53.90,0:12:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got serialized because they judged it \Ncould win over Niizuma's manga, after all.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:00.04,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 7,0:13:02.09,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they took a vote on whether this \Nmanga could win over {\i1}CROW{\i0}\h and {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result was 4 vs. 3 for Lose.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's plenty of potential for you to win from here on out.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it got serialized.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 vs. 3 for lose...
Dialogue: 7,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be enough to just look it over again.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to rewrite it so anyone can agree that we'll win!
Dialogue: 7,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 7,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now! You don't have enough time to rewrite it!
Dialogue: 7,0:13:32.45,0:13:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We'll make it work.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting this zeal into their manga...
Dialogue: 7,0:13:40.61,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 7,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need battles after all?
Dialogue: 7,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}CROW{\i0}\h may have battles,
Dialogue: 7,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}\h has storylines that don't.
Dialogue: 7,0:13:57.34,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, where do you think we're losing to Eiji?
Dialogue: 7,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 7,0:14:03.98,0:14:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say, it would be his expressiveness.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:08.10,0:14:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he uses perspective and sound effects.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings and representations of the \Ncharacters are straightforward and full-bodied,
Dialogue: 7,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his dialogue is polished and easy to understand.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets inside the characters. {}
Dialogue: 7,0:14:18.78,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, you beat him in your \Nsketching. Mashiro's realistic art is better than his.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the sheer amount of Takagi's ideas.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:28.18,0:14:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura, do you have the novel version of {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}\h on you?
Dialogue: 7,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm their editor now, I carry a copy with me.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show it to us?
Dialogue: 7,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote it herself?
Dialogue: 7,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, at Akina's urging,
Dialogue: 7,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be made available soon after the new year.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:50.44,0:14:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the content is pretty much the same as the manuscripts Niizuma received.
Dialogue: 7,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cuts out the unneeded parts in the manuscript...
Dialogue: 7,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and inserts new scenes as necessary.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you compare the two,
Dialogue: 7,0:15:02.42,0:15:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll see that Niizuma's expressiveness made {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}\h much better.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's done so much with it, I'd say this is \Nmore about his imagination than his expression.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Imagination, huh?
Dialogue: 7,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the way he uses the space in his panel layouts...
Dialogue: 7,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panels with no dialogue.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panels with nothing but scenery.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panels where he zooms out and shows the whole picture.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent closeups of characters.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Readers can freely give it their own interpretation.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It engages their imagination.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly...
Dialogue: 7,0:15:36.07,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because I don't put blank panels in my storyboards?
Dialogue: 7,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I put them in myself later,
Dialogue: 7,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're few and far between.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:43.73,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. You both need to consider \Nyour panel choices more carefully.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:48.00,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hattori...
Dialogue: 7,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 7,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We jumped straight into a meeting without officially handing it over...
Dialogue: 7,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't mind that at all.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura...
Dialogue: 7,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even properly thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we work together in the future, please take care of us!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go for it!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try hard, too!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 7,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could come here right away.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, my doubts are gone.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori,
Dialogue: 7,0:16:32.00,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take what you've done with {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0} and use that popularity to my advantage.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bring it on!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:47.73,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping straight into such an \Nadvanced meeting... they're amazing.
Dialogue: 7,0:16:53.69,0:16:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard so that I can reach their level soon!
Dialogue: 7,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Miura, you can take it from here.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start our meeting.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:09.50,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only for work, it's nice to be meeting with such a pretty girl!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:19.76,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you say something like that, I'll sue you for sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 7,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't sue me...
Dialogue: 7,0:17:31.44,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi and Hattori cast me aside...
Dialogue: 7,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall in love anymore!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the best author in the business!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}you{\i0}\h are my editor!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better act like it!
Dialogue: 7,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.42,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really do this?
Dialogue: 7,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.62,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at them!
Dialogue: 7,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawings that get you inside the characters, huh?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting in blank spaces and sound effects, too...
Dialogue: 7,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all difficult.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that hard?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:10.57,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much we revise, I \Ndon't think we can beat Eiji's sense for it.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can let my imagination flow like Eiji's...
Dialogue: 7,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and express Shujin's storyboards better...
Dialogue: 7,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's from Hattori.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going? When do you think you'll have the storyboard done by?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, aren't you on vacation?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until January 6th, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rewriting your storyboard, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to take it easy.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come see it when you're done.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe not on New Year's day.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:48.27,0:18:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that... it feels like we're \Nmaking you go along with our schedule.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori is a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 7,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about on the 2nd?
Dialogue: 7,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't you have to redo 52 pages?
Dialogue: 7,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we'll get it done!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:05.14,0:19:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. I'll contact you after noon on the 2nd.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's here.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miura, the editor who will be taking over {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miura Goro.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were Ashirogi's editor, right?
Dialogue: 7,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to meet you!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:27.82,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However! You shouldn't have made them write a cliché gag manga!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:32.52,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi's all about realistic stories with realistic art!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one they're doing is like that.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}\h!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits them perfectly!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job on getting them there!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Miura!
Dialogue: 7,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 7,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around, Ashirogi will be a tough opponent.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a manga that can compete with mine: {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}.
Dialogue: 7,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it has serious humor along with serious art.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.04,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,And the protagonist must be someone just like Takagi!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:05.04,0:20:08.86,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll do this... and that!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:03.02,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, did you tell him what it was about?
Dialogue: 7,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't tell him anything.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have ESP.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina and Niizuma...
Dialogue: 7,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With them as my partners, I'll definitely grow!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:17.86,0:20:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard so that we don't lose to Ashirogi!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:24.81,0:20:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:27.92,0:20:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagination... blank spaces... and sound effects.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably comes to Eiji naturally.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how he turns a script into a manga.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:38.26,0:20:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shujin's script shouldn't be any worse than Iwase's!
Dialogue: 7,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Takagi?
Dialogue: 7,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mashiro's saying some weird stuff.
Dialogue: 7,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come over and talk to him, if you can.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird stuff?
Dialogue: 7,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying he wants the story in script-only format!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Script only?
Dialogue: 7,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I know how to do paneling now...
Dialogue: 7,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a step backwards?
Dialogue: 7,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a script, I can use my imagination!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:19.14,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel constrained by the storyboard.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:22.85,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)}I'd rather just be given a script so that I can draw freely!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put the blank panels where I want!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if Takagi's okay with it, of course.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for sure if that'll make it better.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:34.93,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe doing it that way will give me more time to write out details on the characters' emotions.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hattori?
Dialogue: 7,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:45.03,0:21:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do it!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I worried about?
Dialogue: 7,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do work well together, after all.
Dialogue: 7,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're relying on me!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:54.65,0:21:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can aim for the top with them!
Dialogue: 7,0:21:58.83,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:00.32,0:22:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started drawing a new one-shot.
Dialogue: 7,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 7,0:22:03.66,0:22:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 7,0:22:04.87,0:22:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}KIYOSHI{\i0}\h's rating is below Master Niizuma and Hiramaru's, and just about even with Aoki's.
Dialogue: 7,0:22:10.93,0:22:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let Ashirogi pass me, too, we won't be the "Fukuda Team" any more!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:15.14,0:22:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still aim higher!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if this one-shot affects your serialization...
Dialogue: 7,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I won't let {\i1}KIYOSHI{\i0}\h slip!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:24.07,0:22:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, that would be...
Dialogue: 7,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write this 45 page one shot while continuing with {\i1}KIYOSHI{\i0}\h as usual.
Dialogue: 7,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw straight through the New Year's holiday without a break!
Dialogue: 7,0:22:35.01,0:22:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. If you're this determined, then I'll support you.
Dialogue: 7,0:22:40.95,0:22:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 7,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 7,0:24:15.01,0:24:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our serialization finally begins!
Dialogue: 7,0:24:16.76,0:24:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely beat Niizuma Eiji!
Dialogue: 7,0:24:18.68,0:24:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Fukuda's one-shot?
Dialogue: 7,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 7,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Votes and Charts.
Dialogue: 7,0:24:24.11,0:24:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,An inherited dream can become even bigger!
Dialogue: 7,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
